proposals.title: Wikiversity to Arabic
proposals.content: I translated the interface and documentation to Arabic.

proposals.title: Wikidata back-end infrastructure
proposals.content: I wrote the core implementation of Wikidata in PHP and MySQL.

proposals.title: Smithsonian content
proposals.content: I posted all of the open content from the Smithsonian Libraries to the Commons with clean metadata.

proposals.title: EOL to Wikispecies
proposals.content: I wrote a bot that syncs Wikispecies with the Encyclopedia of Life.

proposals.title: Epistemology bibliography
proposals.content: I fixed the bibliography of 300 Wikipedia articles in Category:Epistemology.
